OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,FA father and son have been found
OL,7,Fguilty of killing a grandfather in a
OL,8,Fhit-and-run on Teesside.
OL,10,FBrian Darby, 60, was killed when he
OL,11,Fwas hit by a van driven by Martin
OL,12,FBreeze in Ingleby Barwick at around
OL,13,F11.30pm on 2 February. Three other
OL,14,Fpeople were seriously injured.
OL,16,FThe prosecution said he deliberately
OL,17,Ftargeted the group of friends out of
OL,18,Frevenge following an altercation with
OL,19,Fhis son Shaun Breeze as they walked
OL,20,Fhome from the pub.
