OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,FMartin Breeze was high on drink and
OL,7,Fdrugs when he drove into the group.
OL,9,FBoth father and son were accused of
OL,10,Fmurder and attempted murder for the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FFollowing a trial at Teesside Crown
OL,14,FCourt, a jury found Martin Breeze, of
OL,15,FIrthing Close, Ingleby Barwick, guilty
OL,16,Fof murder and four counts of attempted
OL,17,Fmurder.
