OL,6,FShaun Breeze, of Owls Grove, Ingleby
OL,7,FBarwick, was cleared of murder and
OL,8,Fattempted murder but was found guilty
OL,9,Fof manslaughter and three counts of
OL,10,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,11,Fintent.
OL,13,FHe was also found guilty of one count
OL,14,Fof attempting to cause grievous bodily
OL,15,Fharm with intent.
