OL,6,FDuring the trial, the court heard Mr
OL,7,FDarby was carried for 150 metres on
OL,8,Fthe bonnet of Martin Breeze's Citroen
OL,9,FBerlingo which he drove off the road,
OL,10,Facross a grass verge and onto a
OL,11,Ffootpath at around 11.30pm on 2
OL,12,FFebruary.
OL,14,FThe 56-year-old had answered a phone
OL,15,Fcall from his son after he had got
OL,16,Finto a disagreement with the group,
OL,17,Fwho had enjoyed an evening together in
OL,18,Fa local bar.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/12
