OL,6,FMr Darby died at the scene while three
OL,7,Fothers were seriously hurt and another
OL,8,Fnarrowly avoided being struck.
OL,10,FDuring the trial, the court heard that
OL,11,FShaun Breeze had called his father
OL,12,Fafter he got into a disagreement with
OL,13,Fa group of people who had enjoyed a
OL,14,Fnight out at a local bar.
OL,16,FThe prosecution said the father and
OL,17,Fson were out for "revenge" when Martin
OL,18,FBreeze drove into the group.
