OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,FThey then dumped the vehicle and went
OL,7,Fback to the home they shared in Owls
OL,8,FGrove.
OL,10,FThe Crown claimed the father was
OL,11,Fencouraged and assisted to pick the
OL,12,Fgroup out by Shaun Breeze.
OL,14,FEarlier this week, Martin Breeze
OL,15,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving but continued to deny the
OL,17,Fcharges of murder, attempted murder
OL,18,Fand perverting the course of justice
OL,19,Fby later claiming the van had been
OL,20,Fstolen.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/12
