OL,6,FShaun Breeze denied all charges
OL,7,Fthroughout the trial.
OL,9,FOutside court, Mr Darby's family said:
OL,10,F"Today's verdict brings some
OL,11,Fsatisfaction for our family and will
OL,12,Fhopefully serve as some justice for
OL,13,FBrian.
OL,15,F"It goes without saying that it will
OL,16,Fnot bring our Brian back, nor lessen
OL,17,Fthe pain and anguish we have suffered
OL,18,Fin losing him and we will continue to
OL,19,Fsuffer forever.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
