OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,F"We would like to thank the members of
OL,7,Fthe public who shared information with
OL,8,Fthe police and those who did
OL,9,Feverything they could to try and save
OL,10,FBrian that night.
OL,12,F"It gives us comfort to know that
OL,13,Fthere are still kind and caring people
OL,14,Fin our community, a stark contrast to
OL,15,Fthose who took his life away and
OL,16,Fthrough their denials put our family
OL,17,Fthrough the pain of a trial in order
OL,18,Fto save themselves.
OL,20,F"For those individuals, we have no
OL,21,Fwords."
