OL,6,FDetective Inspector Matt
OL,7,FHollingsworth, from Cleveland Police's
OL,8,FHomicide and Major Enquiry Team, said:
OL,9,F"Angry with what had taken place,
OL,10,FMartin used the van as a weapon to
OL,11,Fdeliberately drive at the group
OL,12,Fpointed out by Shaun.
OL,14,F"The consequences of this senseless
OL,15,Fact has had a devastating impact on so
OL,16,Fmany people.
OL,18,F"It led to Brian, a well-liked and
OL,19,Fwell-known man in the area he lived,
OL,20,Flosing his life.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
