OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,F"He had been enjoying a night out with
OL,7,Ffriends who were all in high spirits
OL,8,Fas they began walking home.
OL,10,F"Tragically, that came to end when
OL,11,FShaun ` who we believe was out
OL,12,Fpeddling drugs in the area ` barged
OL,13,Finto them.
OL,15,F"What unfolded next was purely an act
OL,16,Fof revenge that resulted in murder.
OL,18,F"The pair then going on to lie and
OL,19,Fdeceive police in an attempt to
OL,20,Fconceal their crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
