OL,3,CFather who drove van into group out of
OL,4,C'revenge' guilty of murder
OL,6,F"However, following swift
OL,7,Finvestigative work we were able to
OL,8,Funpick their version of events and
OL,9,Fbuild an evidential case that
OL,10,Fultimately led to justice for Brian,
OL,11,Fthe other people injured that night
OL,12,Fand their family.
OL,14,F"I would like to express my sincere
OL,15,Fcondolences to Brian's family and
OL,16,Ffriends.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
