OL,6,F"It has been an incredibly difficult
OL,7,Ftime for them, and everyone involved
OL,8,Fin what happened that night. I hope
OL,9,Fthey can in some way start to rebuild
OL,10,Ftheir lives after the pain they have
OL,11,Fall gone through."
OL,13,FBoth men will be sentenced on 2 August.
